text: Dharminder Mann (born May 29, 1984) is an American entrepreneur, video producer, internet personality and YouTuber. He is known for making motivational videos on YouTube, and educating the young generation on the topic of bullying, mistreatment, and underestimation. == Other websites == * * Category:1984 births Category:American YouTubers Category:Businesspeople from Los Angeles Category:Living people
